
 
/!\ Please check carefully the gate closing section before modify it. It includes a security checking to avoid closing the gate on the mouse head if the animal is still in the licking chamber   

 
The only parameters to customize before starting are the opening (max_position_opening) ans closing (max_position_closing) position of the gate servomotor. These values depend on the mounting settings of the gate 


Due to the overflow of Arduino with the function micro(), the session stop after 65min. Before starting a new Session, restart the Arduino

The code contains:
 - White noise generator. 
 - Training stages
 - Posibility to activate a laser on different trial windows
